own.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   真心係扑街物種。<br />\n所以我建議 退而求其次 先換山區兒童 計劃順利再換第三世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddd434a610255dd6fb9ed9592eefefd2bb7125fb","tid":178230,"uid":99073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T13:36:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主你係咪受到刺激先咁憎肥婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係。不過唔講啦 費事勾起大家被肥婆刺激的往事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"816bcb87359d18cf6d97f4ac4238ac6e5aba17ba","tid":178230,"uid":99073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T13:39:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>換三個內地山區兒童較好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為換三個第三世界兒童 問題太多<br />\n反正香港每年都吸收大陸人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不如換d未被深度污染的兒童<br />\n <br />\n試諗下。肥婆飲水都可以肥。究竟要每日飲幾多水先可以到達增肥較果？專家話每日七杯水健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 肥婆可能每日飲七卡倫水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人地山區兒童 一日都唔知有冇一桶水用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  d肥婆居然貪心到研發飲水增肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   真心係扑街物種。<br />\n所以我建議 退而求其次 先換山區兒童 計劃順利再換第三世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"e101dd516cca3776b3854460c3875dd1203e3f84","tid":178230,"uid":82528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T13:41:51.000Z","msg":"但係死肥婆 可以賣波蘿<br />\n咁餓餓兒童有咩貢獻？"},{"pid":"ab10dabb46b8f8e813f82b51a4985c52257db204","tid":178230,"uid":88731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T13:43:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>換三個內地山區兒童較好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為換三個第三世界兒童 問題太多<br />\n反正香港每年都吸收大陸人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不如換d未被深度污染的兒童<br />\n <br />\n試諗下。肥婆飲水都可以肥。究竟要每日飲幾多水先可以到達增肥較果？專家話每日七杯水健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 肥婆可能每日飲七卡倫水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人地山區兒童 一日都唔知有冇一桶水用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  d肥婆居然貪心到研發飲水增肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   真心係扑街物種。<br /